gedu.site/team06</a> to provide a username and email address. Those who engage in transactions with FASHION SHOPPING are asked to provide additional information, including as necessary the personal and financial information required to process those transactions. In each case, FASHION SHOPPING collects such information only insofar as is necessary or appropriate to fulfill the purpose of the visitor''s interaction with FASHION SHOPPING. FASHION SHOPPING does not disclose personally-identifying information other than as described below. And visitors can always refuse to supply personally-identifying information, with the caveat that it may prevent them from engaging in certain website-related activities.\r\n<h3>Aggregated Statistics</h3>\r\nFASHION SHOPPING may collect statistics about the behavior of visitors to its websites. FASHION SHOPPING may display this information publicly or provide it to others. However, FASHION SHOPPING does not disclose personally-identifying information other than as described below.\r\n<h3>Protection of Certain Personally-Identifying Information</h3>\r\nFASHION SHOPPING discloses potentially personally-identifying and personally-identifying information only to those of its employees, contractors and affiliated organizations that (i) need to know that information in order to process it on FASHION SHOPPING behalf or to provide services available at FASHION SHOPPING websites, and (ii) that have agreed not to disclose it to others. Some of those employees, contractors and affiliated organizations may be located outside of your home country; by using FASHION SHOPPING websites, you consent to the transfer of such information to them. FASHION SHOPPING will not rent or sell potentially personally-identifying and personally-identifying information to anyone. Other than to its employees, contractors and affiliated organizations, as described above, FASHION SHOPPING discloses potentially personally-identifying and personally-identifying informatio